{"tid":1366313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南邊圍村民憶述事前很多陌生人出入 村公所以木板圍封","createTime":"2019-07-26T02:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T02:53:14.000Z","uid":23707,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bab919e2ca60a6b92ac06bb92ba02b97de5b1f1a","tid":1366313,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/YL-FOLO-190725-12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FYL-FOLO-190725-12.jpg&h=abeb4e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyvOdgA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcyvOdgA.png&h=6e002371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=356695&amp;hot=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356695%26hot%3D1&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=adeee3c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356695%26hot%3D1&h=f3426f53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=356695&amp;hot=1</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】元朗襲擊事件當晚大批白衣人在南邊圍聚集，有村民憶述當天很多陌生人出入，有原居民擔心有人發起光復元朗行動會令無辜村民受牽連。<br />\n<br />\n元朗襲擊事件當晚大批白衣人退守到南邊圍，在村公所前聚集。事隔數天來到，村公所的玻璃窗都用木板圍封起。<br />\n<br />\n有村民帶我們入村，憶述當晚有很多穿白衣的陌生人在村內進出，懷疑這些人都不是村民。<br />\n<br />\n她稱在襲擊事件發生前，不察覺村民間有討論，但在元朗一帶多次收到「溫馨提示」。<br />\n<br />\n針對襲擊事件，有團體發起周六「光復元朗」遊行，有原居民擔心南邊圍村會被針對，殃及無辜村民。有村民稱，已購備乾糧，遊行當日留在家中以策安全，亦已提醒子女出入要多加留意。<br />\n<br />\n南邊圍村原本有多個出入口。有村民指，星期日後其他門都已經鎖上，只剩正門可以出入。而村內亦安排有人通宵在門口把守，以防有陌生人出入。"},{"pid":"03b092179a93972c23b315438904c90ccd69430c","tid":1366313,"uid":23707,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:25:02.000Z","msg":"我哋唔係白衫<br />\n唔好殃及無辜"},{"pid":"cc713c713ad8e1572d2634c4eaba6995c14c48e0","tid":1366313,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:26:39.000Z","msg":"得9閒攪你條村<br />\n係攪都係黑社會攪<br />\n關我地撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff52b93ba8bf1314e210bf0c8a2f15e5af45a6d","tid":1366313,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:28:24.000Z","msg":"好人好姐點解怕"},{"pid":"2656aad4bf157eae00acdbce3eaff76582623689","tid":1366313,"uid":97909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:29:07.000Z","msg":"咁多木材會唔會仲易著火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0033137563d7893169008c41b0401be18031fc","tid":1366313,"uid":268623,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:29:49.000Z","msg":"唔好好似黑社會咁無差別襲擊，我地要記住我地既理念，唔好被仇恨影響"},{"pid":"c9c15e959d2e84f1189c0f22ade600eafdf4d8cf","tid":1366313,"uid":41246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:31:53.000Z","msg":"封晒木板睇唔到入面，會唔會藏有大量武器、危險品? 定係想聽日捉啲市民入去施刑?"},{"pid":"485e5ab0fdd01368d9c361eee9d84ea566fba96c","tid":1366313,"uid":136988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:34:21.000Z","msg":"唔知點解我覺得封木板呢個舉動咁似三國赤壁連還船一樣, 未出事以為自己好撚醒咁"},{"pid":"734d634e2ac5a212f66acf067d769b6d5015171b","tid":1366313,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>立法會有鋼板同強化玻璃啦！<br />\n<br />\n俗語有云：「先撩者賤, 打死無怨」<br />\n<br />\n沒有一個鄉黑係無辜的</strong></span>"},{"pid":"dc7c7a5d64d827a95f8ecf726f27205ecc6c7d20","tid":1366313,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:38:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有天水圍廈村鄧氏出咗200恐怖份子<br />\n<br />\n唔係諗住無人知無人會理掛？<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"096bca323ecaf272ea9682d2efa7dac1d41af892","tid":1366313,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9c15e959d2e84f1189c0f22ade600eafdf4d8cf","tid":1366313,"uid":41246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"